<h3 id="2-super-fast">2. SUPER FAST</h3>

<p>The Bigezo Desktop Application sends messages at a whooping average speed of 100SMS per minute. While sending the SMS, you are able to monitor the sending process using the visual progressbar and labels.</p>

<h3 id="3-reliable-reports">3. Reliable Reports</h3>

<p>At the end of every message sending, Bigezo software generates a report showing key details like:</p>
<ul>
