  <li>How much did you spend?</li>
  <li>At what time were the messages sent?</li>
  <li>Which message was sent to which number?</li>
</ul>

<p>This report is an ordinary text file format <strong>(.txt)</strong>   and is saved on your PC. Bigezo shows you the location of this file.</p>

